# T28 IO Ring Orchestrator — Skill-local .env (OPTIONAL)
#
# In the recommended setup, all config lives in the PROJECT-ROOT .env
# (one file for bridge + T28 + any other skills). See:
#   <project-root>/.env.example
#
# Only create this file if you need skill-specific overrides that differ
# from the project root .env. If both exist, project root is loaded first
# (override=False), so project-level values are not clobbered.
#
# Variables that can go here OR in project root .env:
#
#   CDS_LIB_PATH_28=/absolute/path/to/your/T28/cds.lib
#   VB_FS_MODE=remote
#   AMS_OUTPUT_ROOT=C:/Users/youruser/project/output
#   AMS_IO_AGENT_PATH=/absolute/path/to/workspace
